description: The epitome of the do-it-all down jacket, the Access Down Jacket is their most versatile midweight down insulator that brings the heat for primo fall cragging days, lightweight ski tours and chilly days down in town. New for F19, the jacket’s lofty 700- ll RDS goose down insulation packs down small in your pack or duffel, and zippered hand and chest pockets stash your phone, wallet and other small essentials.
name: Black Diamond Access Down Jacket - Mens
